<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.3.2">
<l>iruntāṉe ṉuḷḷat tiṟaivaṉ kaṟaicēr</l>
<l>paruntāḷ kaḷiṟṟuk karuḷceyta ceṅkaṇ</l>
<l>peruntōḷ neṭumālaip pērpāṭi yāṭa</l>
<l>varuntāteṉ koṅkai yoḷimaṉṉu maṉṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The glisten remains on my breasts which are not gaunt</l>
<l>When I dance and sing the names of tall, bright-eyed Māl</l>
<l rend="indent">with broad shoulders,</l>
<l>Who granted grace to the elephant, [its] thick legs like mortars,</l>
<l>[My] god, the one who is in my heart. Oh, wonder!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
